 switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Ticket","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"d90bdd03-41b1-897a-9422-c504bec0022d","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Ticket\n\nShapes the item: writes `ticketId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"dceb0159-1815-df8e-2d55-23866588136b","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Ticket"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.ticketId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reason & Act (AI Agent) · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"e26c1d55-68d3-ca46-135e-67438aaf3e92","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"61fd5193-09af-846b-d9a5-df2648d28434","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Reason & Act (AI Agent)\n\nThe AI brain: reads the input, decides which attached tools to call (and in what order), then composes the answer.\n\nPorts: ①→ Shape Agent Output · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"64fa9f97-cd41-87c5-a3bd-8116f6dbdac0","name":"Note: Reason & Act (AI Agent)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenRouter Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenRouter API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1090],"id":"0414108f-403f-9e36-1d4b-46f5c3818eb4","name":"Note: OpenRouter Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Think It Through\n\nScratchpad tool: lets the agent reason step-by-step before acting.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1510],"id":"a61403ed-3f8f-4f0d-6af2-1c541dde06b0","name":"Note: Think It Through"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Custom Logic Tool\n\nDeterministic code helper the agent can invoke for exact computation.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1114,1750],"id":"068998d7-ddd3-50b8-9525-881b3be00081","name":"Note: Custom Logic Tool"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Shape Agent Output\n\nShapes the item: writes `answer`, `confidence`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Confident Enough?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1438,520],"id":"c191b4d6-b34f-5057-0ae0-5324a49d51a9","name":"Note: Shape Agent Output"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Confident Enough?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.confidence }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Deliver Answer + Log to Airtable · ②→ Escalate to Human Queue","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1762,520],"id":"bbf9e193-fdc9-e36a-90a7-5021071632be","name":"Note: Confident Enough?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Deliver Answer + Log to Airtable\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2086,280],"id":"c39db42d-e699-182a-8c0f-2f7d691d1e66","name":"Note: Deliver Answer + Log to Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate to Human Queue\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2410,880],"id":"21bd4315-5e92-7e3e-c93d-d7cfd472d8c6","name":"Note: Escalate to Human Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Join Outcomes\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3058,520],"id":"cd397b86-05d4-e4a6-6dac-3337ac029f49","name":"Note: Join Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Airtable)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4030,520],"id":"69c1c0f3-1fe1-da34-c8ee-e1d77d72fec0","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4354,520],"id":"a93510ab-0a17-959e-696a-cb49cffb4208","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4678,520],"id":"8f73da35-3f53-9de6-7246-72ae7d3d9e54","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4030,1540],"id":"7c9e48cc-2325-17e9-4540-26ac00ab45e2","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4354,1540],"id":"8012a270-e073-9866-a012-fbea6c111fc2","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Digest long emails with Airtable and Telegram on autopilot\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDigest long emails with Airtable and Telegram on autopilot. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual triage is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Stamp & Shape Ticket → Payload Valid? → Reason & Act (AI Agent) → Shape Agent Output → Confident Enough? → Deliver Answer + Log to Airtable → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating triage in customer support\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; OpenRouter API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"47153495-062a-2219-0707-8c4a54b3dad8","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"5738699d-845b-f22e-7e4b-4064f7c08611","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"eccaa636-cd9b-8da7-6ae9-a7c658541cab","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"b880d75d-1f8e-7801-bdcc-87eb5a784f3a","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your triage process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-260],"id":"1a2977ad-d444-d920-0a8b-270e49dd451e","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Ticket","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Ticket":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenRouter Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Think It Through":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Custom Logic Tool":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Reason & Act (AI Agent)":{"main":[[{"node":"Shape Agent Output","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Shape Agent Output":{"main":[[{"node":"Confident Enough?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Confident Enough?":{"main":[[{"node":"Deliver Answer + Log to Airtable","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Escalate to Human Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Deliver Answer + Log to Airtable":{"main":[[{"node":"Join Outcomes","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate to Human Queue":{"main":[[{"node":"Join Outcomes","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Join Outcomes":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Airtable)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Airtable)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"94bfc752-13a3-46c5-9169-84ed4fb593da","id":"FDX09906"}